{"tid":2245532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中學生涉藏伸縮棍 控方堅持起訴不理裁判官意見","createTime":"2020-10-16T09:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T01:20:52.000Z","uid":56115,"like":95,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab3b101b0725467e933de086cb1c8a959765629","tid":2245532,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"17歲中學生被指去年於示威現場藏有一支伸縮棍，被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪。署理主任裁判官溫紹明早前處理案件時，舉例指內地生在中大校園內持刀揮舞表達不滿，被控同樣罪名，最終獲律政司同意以簽保守行為撤控了事，直言「<span class=\"red\">中大揮刀嗰個係大學生，律政司都認為可以放佢一馬，fine！咁我就覺得呢單案有更多原因值得放</span>」，要求雙方商討處理方法。案件今天再提堂，控方堅持檢控。辯方申請擱置聆訊，溫官批准案件押後至12月1日開庭處理相關申請。"},{"pid":"caac25806d689f63ba281c4cae3645e3908adb4b","tid":2245532,"uid":56115,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/EUXTBEK35NFRBPDUEWVPE6CKDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FEUXTBEK35NFRBPDUEWVPE6CKDY%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=782c45b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FEUXTBEK35NFRBPDUEWVPE6CKDY%2F&h=4a8a8a62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/EUXTBEK35NFRBPDUEWVPE6CKDY/</a>"},{"pid":"b5bb397ef1a4d3d202184ba9139e622fe1252939","tid":2245532,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79a7bb26943cc8c8f02bf169c274915353a5e85","tid":2245532,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811311f8ec91251576e84f9359b83c03970f68e7","tid":2245532,"uid":56115,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:52:22.000Z","msg":"中大內地生李丹石（21歲）去年11月7日在中文大學中央校園大學圖書館外持刀揮舞，並高唱中國國歌，原本被控一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，後獲准以2,000元簽保、守行為24個月，另付堂費1,000元了事。署理主任裁判官溫紹明當日多番質疑有關決定，直指「稀有」，又謂「點都嚴重過雷射筆，危險好多」。惟基於撤控與否全憑控方決定，最終只能如此處理。"},{"pid":"eaf0f8d558281de59c1e9679eabe93d4f7f21333","tid":2245532,"uid":26014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:53:05.000Z","msg":"DOJ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971d984686476ac4c83ea4fc9c110a2a4e4f686f","tid":2245532,"uid":1767,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"正常官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd83f82a1fccbaf1ad2c597f8f846c6bd80c4eb2","tid":2245532,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:54:07.000Z","msg":"係另一單定之前嗰單？<br />\n<br />\nBtw佢同錢好似都係無份審國安法？"},{"pid":"16f35c3dae7eac5bedf069b95cc914639163b129","tid":2245532,"uid":56115,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"dd83f82a1fccbaf1ad2c597f8f846c6bd80c4eb2","tid":2245532,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:54:07.000Z","msg":"係另一單定之前嗰單？<br />\n<br />\nBtw佢同錢好似都係無份審國安法？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:55:16.000Z","msg":"之前個單黎, 一直deal緊守行為<br />\n佢只係署理所以亦都冇揀到"},{"pid":"7cb050bd35c71ef856e7286594f4306e6e3fdac9","tid":2245532,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc47b4d165a7b6ad952e0ce17dd4fbabba953ed","tid":2245532,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"伸縮棍可能只係自拍棍"},{"pid":"6811d4f328d77f8efed1d1f595fb9251e985b489","tid":2245532,"